ChangeLog for smooth

dd.mm.yy hh:mm - smooth alpha 0.9.11

- bitmaphaiku.cpp	- fixed bitmap transparency issues
- timerposix.cpp	- fixed potential deadlocks when using POSIX timers with GLib/GTK

